{
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.boss.text": "\\\n当你手持**贝壳号角**并在冰冻深海的海边吹响，船长科妮莉亚亡灵会从水中浮现。\n\\\n\\\n*贝壳号角: 击杀*搁浅舰船*遗迹中待在船长室的掠夺者可获得。*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.boss.title": "船长科妮莉亚亡灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.description": "求生者吹响的稀疏号角自会惊醒她的灵魂。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.entity.text": "\\\n*搁浅舰船: 结构ID为aquamirae:ship*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.captain.name": "船长科妮莉亚亡灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.dragon.boss.text": "",
