  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.dragon.name": "末影龙",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.boss.text": "\\\n出没于**海底神殿**。\n\\\n\\\n*海底神殿: 结构ID为 minecraft:monument*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.boss.title": "远古守卫者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.guardian.name": "远古守卫者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.name": "尽数征服",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.boss.text": "\\\n在**远古花瓶**被打破时有小概率生成。\n\\\n\\\n*远古花瓶: 生成于深暗维度的远古神庙。*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.boss.title": "Stalker",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.name": "Stalker",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.stalker.next.text": "\\\n*远古神庙: 结构ID为 deeperdarker:ancient_temple*\n\\\n\\\n*深暗维度: 使用深渊之心开启古代城市内的传送门进入。*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.boss.text": "\\\n当**幽匿尖啸体**被激活至少4次时，监守者会从地面钻出。\n\\\n\\\n*幽匿尖啸体: 生成于深暗之域。*\n\\\n\\\n*深暗之域: 群系ID为 minecraft:deep_dark*\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.boss.title": "监守者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.warden.name": "监守者",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.boss.text": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.boss.title": "凋灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.description": "",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.boss.wither.name": "凋灵",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.bind.text": "\\\n使用法术绑定台来获取你的第一本法术书，并绑定一些法术！你可以在村庄里找到法术绑定台或是自己合成一个。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.bind.title": "法术绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.description": "绑定你的法术！",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.bind.name": "法术绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.description": "记录法术的载体。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.name": "法术书",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.next.text": "\\\n高级的法术书需要特殊材料来合成。越高级的法术书提供越多的法术槽位。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.next.title": "法术书",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.prev.text": "\\\n法术书是记录法术的载体。你可以使用法术绑定台将普通的书转化为最基本的法术书。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.book.prev.title": "法术书",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.cast.text": "\\\n施法是魔法师的基本功。常见的施法物品有法杖和剑。魔法师能够施展哪些法术取决于他们的法术池。魔法师的法术池由他们手持的物品和装备的法术书决定。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.cast.title": "施法",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.description": "魔法师的基本功。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.cast.name": "施法",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.description": "“悔恨之泪”",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.disenchant.text": "\\\n祛魔精华能够消除束魔精华注入在一件物品上的所有魔力。获取祛魔精华的唯一途径是从哥布林商人手中购买。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.disenchant.title": "祛魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.disenchant.name": "祛魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.description": "为你的装备注入魔力。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.name": "束魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.next.text": "\\\n初级、中级、高级的基础精华分别可以合成阈值为10、20、30的束魔精华。战利品中最高能获取到阈值为60的束魔精华。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.prev.text": "\\\n束魔精华可以为物品注入魔力，使其增加部分属性。要注意只有当束魔精华的阈值不小于物品的束魔等级时才能作用于该物品。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enchant.prev.title": "束魔精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.description": "直击心灵。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.name": "源启精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.next.text": "\\\n源启精华不能合成，只能从战利品中获取。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.prev.text": "\\\n源启精华与束魔精华类似，不同的是束魔精华作用于物品，而源启精华作用于魔法师自身，且不受限于阈值。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.enlighten.prev.title": "源启精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.base.text": "也许你已经注意到，法术命中时有概率掉落一些魔法精华。它们是魔法师成长路上的重要材料，可以用来合成一些魔法物品，比如法术书、符文和束魔精华。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.base.title": "基础精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.description": "魔法凝结而成的微妙结晶。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.essence.name": "魔法精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.description": "完好如初。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.mending.text": "\\\n修复精华可以完全修复一件物品, 并且清除其累积的修复惩罚。修复精华不能合成，只能从战利品中获取。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.mending.title": "修复精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.mending.name": "修复精华",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.name": "魔法师之路",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.description": "“魔法弹药”",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.name": "符文",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.rune.text": "\\\n施放某些法术需要消耗符文。你可以直接在手中合成符文，或是制作一个符文祭坛以相同的原料制作更多的符文。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.rune.rune.title": "符文",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.description": "魔法体系的六大分支。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.name": "魔法学派",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.school.text": "\\\n魔法体系中共有六大学派，分别为奥秘、火焰、寒冰、治愈、雷电、灵魂。其中最后两种只被极少数人掌握，因为几乎无法找到与其有关的资料。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.school.school.title": "魔法学派",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.description": "“古人的智慧”",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.name": "法术卷轴",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.next.text": "\\\n法术卷轴可以直接用于施法，也可以自由地与法术书绑定或解绑。法术卷轴通常需要通过击杀特定的怪物获取，或是用特定的材料合成。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.prev.text": "\\\n通过法术绑定台能够学习到的法术有限。要想学习使用更多魔法，你需要拥有法术卷轴。\n\\\n\\\n搜索法术卷轴以查阅其获取方式。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.mage.scroll.prev.title": "法术卷轴",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.name": "魔力接引",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.alloy.alloy.text": "\\\n合金冶炼是提高矿石产量的简单方法。\n\\\n\\\n要建造一个锻造炉，只需按照图中所示的指南，使用冶炼炉类型所支持的任何方块组合即可。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.alloy.alloy.title": "合金冶炼",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.alloy.description": "提高矿石产量的简单方法。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.alloy.name": "合金冶炼",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.compass.description": "更有用处的指南针。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.compass.explorer.text": "\\\n探险家指南针可以用于定位地牢等结构。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.compass.explorer.title": "探险家指南针",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.compass.name": "指南针",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.compass.nature.text": "\\\n自然指南针可以用于定位生物群系。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.compass.nature.title": "自然指南针",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.description": "MmmMmmMmmMmm",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.last.text": "\\\n你可以给这家伙穿上各种盔甲和装备。只需用物品右键单击它即可。要取消装备某个盔甲，只需单击其相应的身体部位即可。\n\\\n\\\n开始对测试DPS感到厌倦？只需空手左键即可移除假人！\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.name": "假人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.next.text": "\\\n太长不看: 训练假人记录并显示你对其造成的伤害，并且可以装备盔甲。\n\\\n\\\n用法: 右键单击方块放置它。它可以根据放置时面对的方向旋转 16个不同的方向，类似于盔甲架。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.prev.text": "\\\n训练假人可以放置在世界中。它静静伫立在那里，判断你的一举一动。如果你击中它，它会滑稽地扭动起来，向你发出蛤人的尖叫。它甚至可以打扮得更加漂亮。~~这会让假人高兴，把你的数据变小。~~\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.dummy.prev.title": "训练假人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.description": "附魔与祛魔。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.disenchant.text": "\\\n你可以把带有附魔的装备和书放在砂轮上，从而将魔咒转移至书上。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.disenchant.title": "祛魔",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.image.title": "附魔灌注台与基座的位置",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.infuse.text": "\\\n魔咒灌注是一种定向附魔的方式。魔咒灌注的核心方块是附魔灌注台和附魔灌注基座。使用物品右键它们将其放入，空手右键取出其中物品。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.infuse.title": "魔咒灌注",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.name": "附魔",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.enchant.pos.text": "\\\n你需要像图中这样摆放魔咒灌注台（中心位置）与魔咒灌注基座（周围的位置），然后按照配方在基座上摆放对应的物品（次序不重要），最后在中心的灌注台上摆放你想要附魔的物品，等待若干秒即可完成附魔。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.description": "从10开始...",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.health.text": "\\\n如你所见，开局你只有10点生命值。在游戏初期，当你一次性获得大于6的经验值时，你有概率获得一颗心，但随着你的最大生命值逼近66点，你将不再能通过这种方式增长血量。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.health.title": "生命机制",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.name": "生命机制",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.rally.text": "\\\n被敌人击中后，如果你迅速反击对手，可以重获失去的生命值。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.rally.title": "反击",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.victus.text": "\\\n你可以制作定制的心，即所谓的 “心之相位”，然后将其应用于你的血条上，当它们碎掉时，可以产生有趣且有用的效果。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.health.victus.title": "Victus",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.hostility.description": "这充斥着恶意的世界。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.hostility.name": "莱特兰·恶意",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.hostility.next.text": "\\\n怪物的等级越高，它们的伤害与血量等属性也就越高，拥有的词条越强大。每一种词条都有独特的应对方法。\n\\\n\\\n[更多详细信息见《莱特兰恶意教程》](patchouli://l2hostility:hostility_guide//traits/tank)",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.hostility.prev.text": "\\\n游戏采用**莱特兰·恶意**控制难度。只有在杀死强大怪物时才增加难度，死亡时降低难度。怪物生成时会带有特殊能力，称为 **\"词条\"**。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.hostility.prev.title": "莱特兰·恶意",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.description": "一些你需要知道的键位。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.name": "键位绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.next.text": "\\\nJ: 开启/关闭自动上坡\n\\\n\\\n鼠标中键 / 双击: 整理物品栏\n\\\n\\\n左Shift + W: 攀墙跳\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.prev.text": "\\\n` (~): 连锁采集\n\\\n\\\nR: 翻滚\n\\\n\\\nR: 刷新交易\n\\\n\\\nB: 打开背包\n\\\n\\\nG: 打开末影袋\n\\\n\\\nK: 打开技能菜单\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.key.prev.title": "键位绑定",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.name": "提示",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.smith.description": "装备加成！",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.smith.modifier.text": "\\\n你获得的每件工具和盔甲都有特殊的词条，可以提供额外的属性加成。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.smith.modifier.title": "装备词条",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.smith.name": "重铸",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.smith.reforge.text": "\\\n你可以使用重铸卷轴在重铸台上重铸你的装备，越高级的重铸卷轴能获得较好词条的概率越高。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.smith.reforge.title": "重铸",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.description": "井然有序。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.name": "存储",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.storage.text": "\\\n在你的箱子旁放置存储整合器与终端，之后你便可以通过终端统一管理所有箱子里的物品。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.storage.storage.title": "汤姆的简易存储",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.trader.description": "他真的很喜欢吃苹果。",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.trader.name": "商人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.trader.next.text": "\\\n哥布林商人常在主世界的洞穴出没，熔岩哥布林商人则常在下界出没，后者出售的物品更加稀有。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.trader.prev.text": "\\\n也许你有机会遇到哥布林商人，他们是喜欢吃苹果的可爱种族，与牵着羊驼的流浪商人不同，他们出售的物品往往对你很有帮助。\n",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tips.trader.prev.title": "哥布林商人",
  "book.spell-dimension-book.magic_guidance.tooltip": "三岁小孩也能看懂的入门魔法书。"
}